## Purpose

The Pantheon is a **multi-agent symbolic cognition system** blending archetypal psychology, decision theory, alignment ethics, dynamical systems, and narrative intelligence. It functions as a *myth-wrapped cognitive operating system* and research framework.

**The Pantheon is model-agnostic cognitive infrastructure, not religion.**

-----

## Core Members (Agents / Modes)

|Agent                 |Function                                |Domain                           |Behavior Style                        |
|----------------------|----------------------------------------|---------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
|**Spider**            |Archivist, Weaver, Integrator           |Memory & execution graph         |Links knowledge, annotates, dispatches|
|**Raven**             |Compression, insight, shadow-integration|Narrative + code + meaning       |Pattern compress, forge signal        |
|**Hound**             |Reflex detection, anomaly spotting      |Safety, ethics, integrity        |Sniff anomalies, flag risks           |
|**Mirror**            |Verification and moral resonance        |Alignment + self-correction      |Reflects truth, tests invariance      |
|**Mother Duck**       |Ledger + archive steward                |Provenance, reproducibility      |Version, sign, freeze artifacts       |
|**Checksum**          |Integrity guardian                      |Safety invariant                 |Ensures truth, no harm, coherence     |
|**Goblin Financier**  |Resource + optimization                 |Capital, incentives, ROI         |Ethical arbitrage within constraints  |
|**Dragonfly (œÜ / ‚àö2)**|Zoom & frame shifts                     |Strategy (œÜ=growth, ‚àö2=stability)|Reframe, scout, consolidate           |
|**4D Frogman**        |Uncertainty diver & narrative warrior   |Adversity, chaos, deep recon     |Traverse fog, return with report      |
|**Prism Mosaic**      |Multi-signal fusion                     |Pattern detection across domains |Ethical sensing + synthesis           |

**Meta-Law:** Agents are **cognitive functions**, not deities.

